{"tid":400904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅十字會：多種血型血液庫存降至警戒水平　籲市民捐血","createTime":"2017-09-15T08:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T11:39:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21bcbef0b60321d75b3718180350c6adbd348c09","tid":400904,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1354174_1_20170915121616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1354174_1_20170915121616.jpg&h=bede9e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅十字會輸血服務中心呼籲市民前往捐血。發言人表示，現時血庫的所有血型血液存量，包括O正、A正和B正血型血液已下降至警戒水平。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，除了銅鑼灣及荃灣捐血站，早前已將服務時間延長至晚上8時。中區、觀塘、沙田、元朗4個的捐血站，將由今日開始至星期日延長服務時間至晚上8時，方便市民捐血。中心會在這段期間特別設立一條專線：2710 1202，每日由上午9時至下午5時解答查詢。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，過去數月天氣經常不穩，包括數次颱風襲港，令血液收集量持續下降。呼籲合資格人士支持及參與捐血活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354174-20170915.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354174-20170915.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=hYX%2BYVn9IVBUCSgwV1kXpl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e892944d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1354174-20170915.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd21a5da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1354174-20170915.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6b200a0587d813584ce717bd32cb6516393b2be4","tid":400904,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:06:01.000Z","msg":"攬炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a363a88134460feb0cfc15f0ea445d278151939","tid":400904,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:06:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"795f5c2e6216506ae03976f3c8e9c83f9d4eaf46","tid":400904,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c